Why we should join clubs?

  • You can get exposed more!
  • It enriches your life as a student.
  • You'll grow faster than you think.
  • It's the best way to meet people.
  • The experience will make your CV more interesting!
  • It provides you with a great opportunity to network.

Joining a student organization presents many opportunities to learn more about yourself, your goals, and your strengths. You can learn from how other students handle certain situations and test your current knowledge.

-Myat Min Soe(head of tech club)
